### Version
2.6.10

### Reproduction link
[https://jsfiddle.net/po0jg4us/](https://jsfiddle.net/po0jg4us/)







### Steps to reproduce
# 1、注册全局指令 `v-class`

```js
Vue.directive('class', function (el, binding) {
    el.classList.add(binding.value);
});
```

# 2、注册全局组件 `demo-comp`
```js
Vue.component('demo-comp', {
    template: '<div v-class="\'comp\'"></div>'
});
```

# 3、实例化 Vue，使用字符串模板
```js
new Vue({
    el: '#app',
    template: '<demo-comp class="app"></demo-comp>'
});
```

# 4、最终结果：
```html
<div class="app"></div>
```


### What is expected?
期望 div 上有 `app` 和 `comp` 两个样式类

### What is actually happening?
结果只有 `app` 一个样式类

